<DOC><DOCNO>WSJ910422-0176</DOCNO><DOCID>910422-0176.</DOCID><HL>   Coda Energy to Buy Properties</HL><DATE>04/22/91</DATE><SO>WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), PAGE A9B</SO><CO>   CODA MOB</CO><MS>ENERGY (ENE)</MS><IN>OIL, INTEGRATED MAJORS (OIL)OIL, SECONDARY (OIS)PETROLEUM (PET)TENDER OFFERS, MERGERS, ACQUISITIONS (TNM)</IN><NS>ACQUISITIONS andamp; MERGERS, TAKEOVERS, BOARD BATTLES (TNM)</NS><RE>TEXAS (TX)VIRGINIA (VA)</RE><LP>   DALLAS -- Coda Energy Inc. said it agreed to purchasecertain oil and gas properties in Upton County, Texas, fromMobil Corp. of Fairfax, Va. Terms weren't disclosed.   It is estimated that about 1.3 million barrels of oil and817 million cubic feet of natural gas are recoverable fromthe properties. The transaction is expected to close in May.</LP><TEXT/></DOC>